      <div class="msgContentFrame">That is a good idea. <br /> <br />Another idea I would like to present is some way of assigning a specific pad button to the &quot;default&quot; standard attack action. That way you don't have to scroll the Action bar every time you want to use the standard attack. Because there are various types of standard attacks, you should be able to customize which attack you want to assign for the button.  <br /> <br />I think it would make the gameplay for pad users much more sensible and free them to only use the action bar (which could be on a 3x3 square now with no need for the standard attack to take one space) for special skills and spells.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>SE: <br /><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">Quote:</div><div class="orig">We don't really want to compete against World of Warcraft or for example the new Star Wars MMO.</div></div> <br /></div></div>
